sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Server as MatchManager
  participant Engine as @phalanxduel/engine
  participant Repo as match-repo
  participant DB as Postgres
  participant Replay as replayGame / log readers

  Server->>Engine: Apply validated action
  Engine-->>Server: PhalanxTurnResult + derived events
  Server->>Repo: appendTransactionLog(matchId, action, hashes, events)
  Repo->>DB: INSERT transaction_logs row
  Server->>Repo: saveMatchState(matchId, postState)
  Repo->>DB: UPDATE matches snapshot
  Replay->>DB: SELECT ordered transaction_logs rows
  Replay->>Engine: Re-apply action stream
  Engine-->>Replay: Reconstructed GameState + verification outcome
